# Demo clip shipped with the repo so `dsl run loudness_monitor`
# works out of the box on a clean install (numpy only — no librosa,
# no MP3 codec, no llvmlite). The generator script lives next to it.
!samples/thunderstorm.wav
!samples/make_thunder.py
